{
  "stem": "10181.1",
  "chunk_idx": 13,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I mean, people were actually-- you know, the SS and SA, they were actually organized by the government and-- and had faculties to come and do this.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You know, it wasn't left to the local populace like these so-called-- so-called popular programs, which you read about in Poland, which, also, were organized, but different.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It was organized locally.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "This was, actually, a government order, you know, basically.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And-- and I guess, people were taken by surprise because this was done-- it was prepared like overnight, or I imagine.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "You know.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I mean, I don't know the details, but it was very violent.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Of course, a lot of men over the age of 17, I think, were taken to concentration camps-- you know, to Dachau and Buchenwald.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "My grandfather was taken away.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That I remember.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He was beaten up and was taken away.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, the same day, not the next day--",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, yeah, I didn't see him.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That same day, I didn't see him.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And-- but I saw him again, afterwards, in Holland.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He came to Holland afterwards.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "OK.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He was let go because of his age.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And also, I-- I think, he was let go because always someone along the line-- in those days, especially, there always was an old soldier who would remember and say to himself, how can I do this to this friend of mine who-- who was with me?",
      "word_count": 47
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Because my grandfather, also, served in the army.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "He might not have been in-- I don't think he was in the First World War anymore, but he was in the German Army like everybody else, and he had a lot of people he knew who had been with him in the army.",
      "word_count": 44
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So he was let go after awhile.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "OK.",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
